<h2>Product submitted for review</h2>

<p>
  <strong><%= productTitle %></strong> from <strong><%= vendorName %></strong> has been submitted to the product review queue.
</p>

<p style="margin:16px 0 0;">
  Seller: <strong><%= vendorName %></strong><br />
  Fulfilment: <strong><%= fulfillmentLabel %></strong><br />
  Product code: <strong><%= productCode || 'Not supplied' %></strong>
</p>

<p style="margin:16px 0 0;">
  Please review this product in the admin product review queue.
</p>

<p style="margin:16px 0 0;">
  <a href="<%= reviewUrl %>" style="color:#0f80c3;text-decoration:underline;">Open product review queue</a>
</p>
